721994f-a.text:
Oliver Street, east side, north from but not including Madison Street, to and including Chatham Sduare. The view shows Public School No. 1 on the S.E. corner of Henry Street, with the Baptist Mariner's Temple on the N.E. corner. The Chatham Square Station of the Second and Third Aves., Elevated Lines is shown in the background.
September 7, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
